# Cloned source corpora and the LLVM/Clang fork + build are large and must NOT be
# committed to the proposal repo. Only scripts, matchers, tests, and findings are tracked.

repos/*
!repos/.gitkeep

clang/*
!clang/.gitkeep

# Scan intermediates
**/compile_commands.json
*.log
*.tmp

# findings/ holds the evidence and IS committed (per CLAUDE.md: "the underlying hits saved
# alongside" every number). The ONE exception is the multi-MB raw denominator dump, which is
# fully regenerable with scan_ripgrep.sh — keep it out of git.
findings/raw/_all_override_decls.txt

# Build/test artifacts
*.o
*.obj
a.out
